00:20:58.180 --> 00:20:59.670
Let's start with
the atomic mass.

00:20:59.670 --> 00:21:04.290
If you notice, the atomic
mass is slightly less than 32,

00:21:04.290 --> 00:21:07.950
32 being the mass number, or
