00:45:25.338 --> 00:45:29.410
the fifth or sixth
decimal place.

00:45:29.410 --> 00:45:32.070
But just for exactness,
I stuck on it.

00:45:32.070 --> 00:45:34.470
Yeah, in your calculations,
