00:45:39.780 --> 00:45:44.460
on the table to within 16
electron volts for a total

00:45:44.460 --> 00:45:45.180
of-- yeah--

00:45:45.180 --> 00:45:46.380
271 MeV.

00:45:46.380 --> 00:45:47.790
That's pretty accurate.

00:45:47.790 --> 00:45:48.480
Yeah.

00:45:48.480 --> 00:45:49.980
AUDIENCE: If you
