00:46:01.960 --> 00:46:04.860
So once you can calculate
either the excess mass,

00:46:04.860 --> 00:46:08.753
or the binding energy, or the
total mass of any nucleus,

00:46:08.753 --> 00:46:10.170
you can start to
put them together

00:46:10.170 --> 00:46:11.340
into nuclear reactions.

00:46:11.340 --> 00:46:14.500
So since you asked, let's
take a quick look at them.

00:46:14.500 --> 00:46:16.772
Where is our nuclear
reaction board?

